<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-33-1151 </DOCNO><TEXT>The question is discussed of crack detection of materials and welded jointsin WWER nuclear power plants. As concerns personnel a decision has beentaken in observance of a government decree to establish in every nuclearpower plant locality a unit of specially trained personnel of 35 forevery four WWER-440 units. In-service inspection must involve specialgroups and organizations which supply the respective equipment to theplant. Attention it centred on equipment for such activity and on organizationaland technical aspects relating to routine and general repairs and overhaulswhich include in-service crack detection, on the control of crack detectioninspection by a superior body. (Z.M.).</TEXT></DOC>